FT  24 DEC 92 / More tour groups cut holiday prices
LUNN POLY, Pickfords and Thomas Cook yesterday followed Thomson, Owners
Abroad and Airtours in attempting to stimulate the sluggish holiday market.
Lunn Poly is offering 10 per cent discounts on holidays booked between
December 28 and January 2 up to a total of Pounds 1m a day, while Pickfords
is cutting the price of an average package by about 10 per cent.
Thomas Cook said that from December 28 all bookings would need only a Pounds
1 deposit.
